    "On the CoNaLa dataset, it achieves a BLEU score of 32.46, an exact match accuracy of 12.4%, SacreBLEU of 29.48, and a ROUGE score of 43.95.",
    "Similarly, on the DJANGO dataset, it attains a BLEU score of 56.55, an exact match accuracy of 76.78%, SacreBLEU of 29.48, and a ROUGE score of 43.95.",
    "These results indicate the model's ability to generate code solutions that closely align with human-written code while maintaining linguistic fluency and capturing critical code semantics.",
    "The third model, ELECTRAMarian, combines the powerful ELECTRA encoder with the Marian decoder.",
    "On the CoNaLa dataset, it achieves a BLEU score of 30.18, an exact match accuracy of 10.0%, SacreBLEU of 27.15, and a ROUGE score of 42.42."
